Looking for your “Pan African Lover” or maybe it’s your “Continental Jollof” you need? The duo of  Senegalese pop star Queen Biz and Nigeria’s Chidinma Ekile have him right here. Marking her entry into the Nigerian music space, Queen Biz is making a bold statement with her “Pan African Lover” track which is a beautiful collaboration with Chidinma. The music stars bring their vocal dexterity and unique vocals to the love song as they express their love for their men on the Teekay Witty produced track. The video for the song was shot by Stanz Visuals and it is a catchy tune that would have you dreaming of love and all the finery that comes with it. Listen to the track below and the accompanying video. 